text: Theodore G. "Ted" Venetoulis (June 14, 1934 â€“ October 7, 2021) was an American politician. He was a member of the Democratic Party. He was the sixth Baltimore County Executive from 1974 to 1978. He ran for Governor of Maryland in 1978 but lost the Democratic primary election to Harry Hughes. Venetoulis died on October 7, 2021 at the age of 87.
